snippet.title: The Miner Digs - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A fast paced rogue-lite mining game about taking back what is yours. Even if you'll use it itself to take it back!

Play now for FREE: https://youkaifox.itch.io/

Follow Youkai Fox:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/YoukaiFox


Video music "Moving Right Along" by opengameart.org/users/wolfgang
